longBusinessSummary: Global Clean Energy, Inc. operates as a waste-to-energy alternative fuels company in North America. It focuses on developing build-own-operate waste-to-energy conversion sites that converts waste into energy in the end-of-life plastic, tires, and platinum group metal recover verticals. The company is headquartered in Humble, Texas.
